Property, clear the properties in finally. Avoid YAML/JSON/TOML/HOCON examples unless the test intentionally adds the corresponding optional Hoplite format module.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The README's getting-started examples often use YAML, but hoplite-core alone only includes the Java properties parser; YAML/JSON/TOML/HOCON require optional Hoplite modules and are not necessary for core coverage.\",\n    \"Version 3.0.0 changes environment-variable mapping and default property-source behavior, so tests using ConfigLoaderBuilder.default() can be affected by ambient CI environment or system properties; explicit property sources are safer.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ae5dc1b33be36c4016a3f1783108c8190ba368538ad0c46a7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 6527, "output": 1485, "cacheRead": 41984, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 49996, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782519666524, "responseId": "resp_0ae5dc1b33be36c4016a3f1772f76c8190bbfe0bd5a8266304"}, "toolResults": []}
